This paper deals with network traffic analysis and user tracking, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and computer networks (cs.NI). The use of NetFlow records for analysis suggests a focus on network infrastructure (cs.SI) and data structures (cs.DS). The mention of refining existing tools and developing new ones suggests a possible focus on multimedia (cs.MM) as well.
